_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Patrick Tam Yiu-Man (Chinese: 譚耀文; born 19 March 1969) is a Hong Kong actor and singer.","name":"Patrick Tam Yiu-Man","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"谭耀文，香港男歌手、演员。1988年参加第七届新秀歌唱大赛获得冠军，同届季军为郑秀文。后来在1993年与无线电视签约，转往戏剧发展。1999年，他转往亚洲电视，饰演《纵横四海》中的大反派明智杰。因强烈的戏剧张力与自身突出的演技，成功开启演艺事业的一个高峰。期后他参与许多电影与内地电视演出，更凭《野兽刑警》中的精湛演出，荣获香港电影金紫荆奖和香港电影金像奖的最佳男配角，演技备受认同。他一度于2003年回巢无线电视。 从2009年起谭耀文做回自己的经纪人，并开始在内地全面发展，2012年还签约了首间内地经纪公司拉风娱乐，同时也将会逐渐把重心转向内地电影制作，争取塑造更多经典的荧幕角色。","name":"谭耀文","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"담요문","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"譚耀文，香港男歌手、演員。1988 年參加第七屆新秀歌唱大賽獲得冠軍，同屆季軍為鄭秀文。後來在 1993 年與無線電視簽約，轉往戲劇發展。1999 年，他轉往亞洲電視，飾演《縱橫四海》中的大反派明智傑。因強烈的戲劇張力與自身突出的演技，成功開啟演藝事業的一個高峰。期後他參與許多電影與內地電視演出，更憑《野獸刑警》中的精湛演出，榮獲香港電影金紫荊獎和香港電影金像獎的最佳男配角，演技備受認同。他一度於 2003 年回巢無線電視。\n\n從 2009 年起譚耀文做回自己的經紀人，並開始在內地全面發展，2012 年還簽約了首間內地經紀公司拉風娛樂，同時也將會逐漸把重心轉向內地電影製作，爭取塑造更多經典的熒幕角色。","name":"譚耀文","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Đàm Diệu Văn","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"譚耀文","primary":false}}]}},"person_4205520_translations":{"at":1772647201479,"data":{"id":4205520,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chatchapon Pranotphong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ชัชพล ประณตพงศ์","primary":true}}]}},"tv_129272_credits":{"at":1772647204579,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":4478964,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"高峰","original_name":"高峰","popularity":0.0788,"profile_path":null,"character":"导演","credit_id":"65a28b7b297338012d12e668","order":0}],"crew":[],"id":129272}},"person_1516593_translations":{"at":1772647214070,"data":{"id":1516593,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lang Yueting was born in 1985 in Dalian, Liaoning, China. She graduated from the Central Conservatory of Music. She is an actress and pianist, known best for her roles in \"Mountain Cry\", \"Blind Detective\", and \"Office\".","name":"Lang Yueting","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lang Nguyệt Đình","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"郎月婷","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"郎月婷","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"郎月婷","primary":false}}]}},"person_3337936_translations":{"at":1772647218306,"data":{"id":3337936,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Laura Presgurvic","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Laura Presgurvic","primary":true}}]}},"person_1016433_translations":{"at":1772647227862,"data":{"id":1016433,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kevin Porter","primary":true}}]}},"person_2037815_translations":{"at":1772647227935,"data":{"id":2037815,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Whit Kunschik was born in Oklahoma City, Oklahoma. She is of Native American, Czechoslovakian and Swedish descent.\n\nRaised in a small town with her mother, step-father, and two sisters, her love for film began at a young age when she received her first video camera at the age of 11, piquing her curiosity into filmmaking. She excelled in arts and and athletics, and received a scholarship to play college basketball and would later transfer to the University of Central Oklahoma where she studied Broadcasting and minored in History of Film. Upon graduating she relocated to New York where she studied Meisner Technique and worked on various music videos, commercials, and short films. She has since relocated to Los Angeles and studies at the Bojesse Christopher Truth Be told Actors Collective, a studio where a select group of emerging and notable actors come together each week, surrendering to emotional journey into self discovery, while experimenting with the combined components of Stanislavski's Preparation of Building a Character along with Meisner's Repetition Exercise.","name":"Whit Kunschik","primary":true}}]}},"person_3592937_translations":{"at":1772647229273,"data":{"id":3592937,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이효정","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Hyo-jeong","primary":false}}]}},"person_4186627_translations":{"at":1772647231327,"data":{"id":4186627,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zine Tseng","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primar